{"tid":1321932,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"七二一行動綱領","createTime":"2019-07-15T20:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T00:05:39.000Z","uid":219533,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a4740e2d7d56dbe2938a46eb9ca7e0b4cd7f0e15","tid":1321932,"uid":219533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T20:41:04.000Z","msg":"其實五大訴求係自相矛盾<br />\n<br />\n頭四個訴求係認同現在林鄭政府嘅管治<br />\n<br />\n並要求林鄭答應<br />\n<br />\n如果佢答應又加強林鄭政府嘅合法性<br />\n<br />\n而第五個訴求：立即雙普選<br />\n<br />\n噉林鄭政府馬上解散<br />\n<br />\n一個已經解散嘅政府係無法做撤回撤暴撤控徹查嘅行動<br />\n<br />\n普選勢在必行<br />\n<br />\n小妹認為依家香港人要諗嘅係<br />\n<br />\n香港人成立臨時政府之後<br />\n<br />\n行政上如何處理普選事宜<br />\n<br />\n可以先釋放所有政治犯<br />\n<br />\n推舉梁天琦為臨時香港領袖<br />\n<br />\n領導現有公務員團隊普選立法會<br />\n<br />\n訂立香港憲法<br />\n<br />\n再跟據憲法普選行政機關元首<br />\n<br />\n七二一集會唔洗再叫林鄭回應<br />\n<br />\n佢根本無能力回應<br />\n<br />\n大家討論集中討論香港未來出路"},{"pid":"c67636adef0f90c058ea0501dfd2eb58122d9841","tid":1321932,"uid":219533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T20:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae2523d475cf7e1735ec98ec9594a5838854962","tid":1321932,"uid":219533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T20:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c3fb40937863e721b9fb0fd1869e470418109d","tid":1321932,"uid":219533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T20:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3cfd62226e9e9d3eb14294879f65d335132b54d","tid":1321932,"uid":219533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T20:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f1d766d82c811c1e3c5e636e530cb914d4ed27","tid":1321932,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:05:39.000Z","msg":"其實叫得訴求就已經係跪求緊政府應承，亦等於認同政府嘅正當性"}]}